newApplicationBuilder

public Applications.NewApplicationBuilder newApplicationBuilder(String name)
Creates builder for creating an application that can handle calls and messages for one of your phone number. Many phone numbers can share an application.
Example:
Application application = applications.newApplicationBuilder("appName").incomingCallUrl("http://some_url.com/method").create();
